ants":[{"name":"John","meanings":["As a boy's name this represents a revival of Middle English <i>Jan</i>, a by‐form of   John  , or an adoption of the common European form with this spelling. As a girl's name it is a short form of names such as   Janet   and   Janice ."]},{"name":"Jeane","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Jean ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Jean d'Albret was born in July 1420, in Tartas, Landes, Aquitaine, France, his father, Charles II d'ALBRET, was 23 and his mother, Anne D’Armagnac, was 34. He married Jeanne Catherine de Rohan about 1420, in La Chèze, Côtes-d'Armor, Brittany, France. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died on 3 January 1468, in Nérac, Lot-et-Garonne, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France, at the age of 47."},"et":{"July 1420–3 January 1468":"juuli 1420–3. jaanuar 1468","1418–1485":"1418–1485","1420–1468":"1420–1468","1422–1465":"1422–1465","1426–1473":"1426–1473","1426–Male":"1426–Surnud","1428–1463":"1428–1463","1430–1444":"1430–1444","–Male":"Surnud","1414–1471":"1414–1471","1440–1522":"1440–1522","1397–1471":"1397–1471","1386–1473":"1386–1473","1440":"1440","1473":"1473","1471":"1471","July 1420":"juuli 1420","1426":"1426","1414":"1414","1468":"1468","1522":"1522","1444":"1444","1422":"1422","1465":"1465","1420":"1420","1386":"1386","1397":"1397","1430":"1430","1463":"1463","1485":"1485","3 January 1468":"3. jaanuar 1468","1418":"1418","1417":"1417","1428":"1428","Of, Tartas, Landes, France":"Tartas, Landes, Aquitaine, Prantsusmaa","Tartas, Landes, Aquitaine, France":"Tartas, Landes, Aquitaine, Prantsusmaa","Albret, Bretagne, France":"Bretagne, Prantsusmaa","Nérac, Lot-et-Garonne, Aquitaine, France":"Nérac, Lot-et-Garonne, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"July 1420–3 January 1468":"heinäkuu 1420–3. tammikuuta 1468","1418–1485":"1418–1485","1420–1468":"1420–1468","1422–1465":"1422–1465","1426–1473":"1426–1473","1426–Male":"1426–Kuollut","1428–1463":"1428–1463","1430–1444":"1430–1444","–Male":"Kuollut","1414–1471":"1414–1471